10. BUSINESS RULES
==================================================
Implement and document these rules:

1. Notification must have either templateCode or direct title/message
2. recipientUserId is required
3. EMAIL channel requires recipient email
4. SMS channel requires recipient phone
5. IN_APP can work with only recipient user ID
6. Communication messages must have sender and receiver
7. Communication message text must not be blank
8. Marking as read should set readAt timestamp
9. Only active templates should be used for rendering
10. Booking/payment event notifications should construct meaningful default messages if template is absent

